      <p>Thank you for your interest. Calpe Junior School is a family run  school, established in 1973. The school offers a Co-educational British  Curriculum for pupils aged 3 to 10 years, and is situated in a quiet  residential location, next to the beach and eucalyptus woods in San  Pedro de Alcantara.</p>
      <br />
      <div align="center" style="margin-bottom:10px;"><img src="images/motto.jpg" width="400" height="250" alt="motto" /></div>
