      <p><strong>Our Aims:</strong></p>
      <ol>
        <li>To Provide a friendly, happy, safe and stimulating environment.<br /><br /></li>
        <li>To enable each child to acheive their full potential as an individual.<br /><br /></li>
        <li>Create an atmosphere of trust and caring to enable children to make an effective transition from home to school.<br /><br /></li>
        <li>To provide a balanced programme of learning through the British National Curriculum.<br /><br /></li>
        <li>To foster intellectual, emotional, moral and cultural development.<br /><br /></li>
        <li>To encourage independence and decision making skills.<br /><br /></li>
